title: Easy salmon fish cakes
ingredients: ['1 (418g) tin salmon, drained and flaked', '2 eggs, beaten', '4 tablespoons seasoned dried breadcrumbs', '4 tablespoons instant mashed potato flakes', '1 medium onion, minced', '1 clove garlic, minced', '1/4 teaspoon dried dill', '1/4 teaspoon celery salt', 'salt and pepper to taste', '2 tablespoons olive oil']
